tasks.task: Understand the historical context and specifications of the Case VAC brought into the market for American farmers in 1942.
subtasks: Recognize the year the Case VAC was introduced, 1942.
Learn that the Case VAC was marketed to American farmers.
Note the original cost of the Case VAC in 1955, $1580.
Identify the engine options available with the Case VAC, 2-liter 4-cylinder gasoline or distillate engine.
Determine the production duration of the Case VAC, 13 years.
